Behavior:

| Situation                                                      | Result                                                  |
| -------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------- |
| Generated `.ks` has not been manually changed                  | overwrite normally                                      |
| Generated `.ks` was manually changed and policy is `preserve`  | keep manual file, write regenerated candidate elsewhere |
| Generated `.ks` was manually changed and policy is `overwrite` | overwrite it like normal                                |

