# Tests to run for 6B

Run these inside the VM/container like you have been.

## 1. Syntax test

```bash
CID=pxe-content
SCRIPT=/usr/local/bin/generate-pxe-content.py

podman exec "$CID" python3 -m py_compile "$SCRIPT"
```

## 2. Baseline generate

```bash
podman exec "$CID" python3 "$SCRIPT" --once

curl -fss http://127.0.0.1:18080/ks/rhel8-minimal.ks -o /tmp/rhel8-minimal-before.ks
curl -fss http://127.0.0.1:18080/generated/status.json -o /tmp/status-before.json

python3 -m json.tool /tmp/status-before.json >/dev/null
grep -q '"generated_ks_edit_policy": "preserve"' /tmp/status-before.json
```

## 3. Simulate an emergency manual edit

```bash
podman exec "$CID" /bin/sh -lc '
set -e
echo "# PHASE6B_MANUAL_EDIT_STILL_HERE" >> /etc/nginx/html/ks/rhel8-minimal.ks
grep -q "PHASE6B_MANUAL_EDIT_STILL_HERE" /etc/nginx/html/ks/rhel8-minimal.ks
'
```

## 4. Regenerate and confirm the manual edit was preserved

```bash
podman exec "$CID" python3 "$SCRIPT" --once

curl -fss http://127.0.0.1:18080/ks/rhel8-minimal.ks -o /tmp/rhel8-minimal-preserved.ks
curl -fss http://127.0.0.1:18080/generated/status.json -o /tmp/status-preserved.json

grep -q "PHASE6B_MANUAL_EDIT_STILL_HERE" /tmp/rhel8-minimal-preserved.ks
grep -q '"preserved_manual_edit": true' /tmp/status-preserved.json
grep -q '"manual_edit_detected": true' /tmp/status-preserved.json
```

## 5. Confirm the regenerated candidate was written

```bash
podman exec "$CID" test -f /etc/nginx/html/generated/preserved-kickstarts/rhel8-minimal.ks.candidate
podman exec "$CID" grep -q 'url --url=' /etc/nginx/html/generated/preserved-kickstarts/rhel8-minimal.ks.candidate
```

## 6. Test overwrite mode

```bash
podman exec "$CID" /bin/sh -lc '
set -e
PXE_GENERATED_KS_EDIT_POLICY=overwrite python3 /usr/local/bin/generate-pxe-content.py --once
grep -q "PHASE6B_MANUAL_EDIT_STILL_HERE" /etc/nginx/html/ks/rhel8-minimal.ks && {
  echo "ERROR: overwrite policy did not overwrite manual edit"
  exit 1
} || true
test ! -f /etc/nginx/html/generated/preserved-kickstarts/rhel8-minimal.ks.candidate
grep -q "\"preserved_manual_edit\": false" /etc/nginx/html/generated/kickstart-state/rhel8-minimal.ks.json
'
```

## 7. Return to default preserve mode

```bash
podman exec "$CID" python3 "$SCRIPT" --once

curl -fss http://127.0.0.1:18080/ks/rhel8-minimal.ks -o /tmp/rhel8-minimal-final.ks
